 With an Australian wide tour starting in October, Godskitchen
 celebrates 10 years of bringing the world it&#039;s trance on a global
 scale. With the first disc mixed by John O&#039;Callaghan, he manages to
 set the vibe for the rest of the album. 
 
 Featuring big name trance artists such as Armin van Buuren, Giuseppe 
 Ottaviani, Paul van Dyk, Sied van Riel and many others, it&#039;s definitely
 worth a listen (even if it means to stop listening to the last ASOT
 album.)
